  &bull; Review the Mentor Best Practices (<a href="https://github.com/nodeschool/organizers/wiki/Event-Mentor-Best-Practices">https://github.com/nodeschool/organizers/wiki/Event-Mentor-Best-Practices</a>) wiki page.<br>

